<script>
    function isInNativeApps() {
        if (typeof window === 'object') {
            return (
                (window.webkit &&
                    window.webkit.messageHandlers &&
                    window.webkit.messageHandlers.openAction) ||
                window.__fyndKit
            );
        }
        return false;
    }
    fetch((isInNativeApps() ? "https://api.fynd.com" : "https://www.fynd.com/api") + "/lightspeed/v1/application/current/user/points/history/", {
        headers: {
            Accept: "application/json, text/plain, */*",
            "X-Application-Id": "000000000000000000000001",
            "X-Application-Token": "9502d710-5a22-11e9-a001-57d85417c280",
        }
    }).then(res => res.json()).then(res => {
        console.log("this is the status for refer api", res.status)
        if (!res.page) {
            document.getElementById("yellow-block").style.display = "none";
            return;
        }
        document.getElementById("Fyndpoint").innerText = res.points
    });
</script>
